<div class="banner-feature-section" id="features">
  <div class="uni-page-container text-center">
    <h2>Why Ciclo?</h2>
    <hr class="line-divider">
    <div class="ciclo-image">
      <%= cl_image_tag('o9o8iivj88hfkcywsoz9') %>
    </div>
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="col-sm-12 mt-4">
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Goodbye Bad Roads</h4>
          <p>Get the most up-to-date route information and never run into a bad road again. Follow the trail of fellow Ciclo-ers</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Your Community</h4>
          <p> Ciclo makes it very convenient to get in touch with fellow cyclists around you. Got questions or just want to share experiences over a beer? Reach out through Ciclo.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Peer-reviewed tips</h4>
          <p>Get useful tips from your community. Where are the landmarks? Water fountains? Hidden gems? Ciclo's got your back.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

        <%= link_to "Discover Ciclo", map_path, class: "btn-main uni-box-shadow"  %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

